Detailed Description

Collection of libjpeg-related constants.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum JPEG::ColorSpace
 

Color space conversions.

Enumeration values:
COLOR_UNKNOWN  Unknown or not specified.
COLOR_GRAYSCALE  Monochrome.
COLOR_RGB  Red/green/blue.
COLOR_YCC  Y/Cb/Cr (also known as YUV).
COLOR_CMYK  C/M/Y/K.
COLOR_YCCK  Y/Cb/Cr/K.

enum JPEG::Dither
 

Dither modes for quantization.

Enumeration values:
DITHER_NONE  No dithering, fast and ugly.
DITHER_ORDERED  Ordered dithering, moderate in both.
DITHER_FS  Floyd-Steinberg dithering, flow and pretty.

enum JPEG::Scale
 

Extraction scale factors.

Enumeration values:
SCALE_FULL_SIZE  Extract the full resolution.
SCALE_HALF  Extract at half-resolution.
SCALE_QUARTER  Extract at quarter-resolution.
SCALE_EIGHTH  Extract at eighth-resolution.

enum JPEG::TimeQualityTradeoff
 

Time/quality tradeoff.

Enumeration values:
FASTER  Try to go faster at the expense of quality.
DEFAULT  Use libjpeg's defaults.
BETTER  Try to generate higher quality at the expense of speed.
